description: A simple solution for generating graphs in the DOT language. The output is a textual script that can be visualized and/or converted to an image with external tools. A handy one is a plugin for Visual Studio Code, named Graphviz Preview. There are also online tools like www.webgraphviz.com, where you can paste the script to view your graph.
releaseNotes: An initial, but functional release of the package!
summary: Simple yet versatile library for generating graphs in the DOT language.
title: GiGraph DOT
